{"tid":1394370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實達哥正正係啲人成為中產之後背棄社運既最佳例子","createTime":"2019-08-01T11:35:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T12:16:09.000Z","uid":270383,"like":18,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"59951ee42aaf9f64cc15bd2b89904f062ca36b94","tid":1394370,"uid":270383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:35:03.000Z","msg":"達哥揾到錢之後，名成利就，有錢有女，無論之前幾貼地都好，為左<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">自保</span></span>都逃不開遠離社運。<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有好多pay grade真係高既高級公務員，同埋返左大陸揾真銀既ibanker都係咁。<br />\n<br />\n睇返今日自己身邊，上左岸上左樓既人(曾經2014 佔中) 變成反對示威遊行，驚影響樓價股票。每次自己上街其實都有種莫名其妙既寂寞，一方面感嘆人生高不成低不就，一方面覺得自己冇野輸可以堅持更耐。有時真係好迷茫，覺得個社會真係好有病。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後，8月5 號大家知點做啦</span>"},{"pid":"a5c6ae13dc1b31d5cc1b974b52a56174c8e6e8dc","tid":1394370,"uid":270383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:38:18.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"66f51b4227e22c86b61ccde4a29f0734066c3b1e","tid":1394370,"uid":270383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:39:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"aa5d85fa12b4aef013f067faef956fbf922169ac","tid":1394370,"uid":270383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:42:42.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"cba47722857d3076c55396b6eda97524402f3604","tid":1394370,"uid":259302,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:48:27.000Z","msg":"好多中產都有遊行"},{"pid":"5d0841304f4e2d89303b4996293f8efe74c0a5c2","tid":1394370,"uid":270383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cba47722857d3076c55396b6eda97524402f3604","tid":1394370,"uid":259302,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:48:27.000Z","msg":"好多中產都有遊行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T11:50:58.000Z","msg":"但佢地肯唔肯瞓身？ <br />\n<br />\n達哥都罷工啦，但佢過去呢個月都係好明顯生意同錢行先，社運只係興趣同建立形像。 其他中產都係咁。"},{"pid":"a46099cb87a87b07ce1e933f839c9be245ba3788","tid":1394370,"uid":270383,"like":